Package: ghp
Type: Package
Title: Generalisation of hierarchical partitioning
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stanislaus Stadlmann <stanislaus@stadlmann.cm>
Maintainer: Stanislaus Stadlmann <stanislaus@stadlmann.cm>
Description: This package is a generalisation of hierarchical partitioning, 
    described by Chevan and Sutherland (1991). It can be applied to a variety of
    models with numerous goodness of fit figures to find out which variables
    have the most impact on the dependent variable.
Depends:
        R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
        dplyr (>= 0.7.0),
        combinat (>= 0.0-8),
        Matrix (>= 1.2-10),
        ggplot2 (>= 2.2.0)
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/Stan125/ghp
BugReports: https://github.com/Stan125/ghp/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Suggests: testthat
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
